  ('medical-tech-moex-20651', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-093-aca0a627', 'sub-medical-tech-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關原位癌 (carcinoma in situ) 的觀念，下列何者正確？ 尚無轉移  已侵犯周邊結締組織  為病毒引起  常自然消失', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:15+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "410a76c9c225", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9fe68df2e674", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093020", "c": "105", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床生理學與病理學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 70, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-20652', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-093-aca0a627', 'sub-medical-tech-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '費城染色體 (Philadelphia chromosome) 與下列何種疾病最有關係？ 急性骨髓性白血病 (acute myeloid leukemia)  慢性骨髓性白血病 (chronic myeloid leukemia) 惡性淋巴瘤 (malignant lymphoma)  何杰金氏病 (Hodgkin’s disease)', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:15+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "410a76c9c225", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9fe68df2e674", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093020", "c": "105", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床生理學與病理學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 71, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-20653', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-093-aca0a627', 'sub-medical-tech-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者為良性腫瘤最重要的特徵？ 異型有絲分裂數目增加  對鄰近組織有侵襲性或浸潤  會產生衛星性小腫瘤  不會轉移到別的器官', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:15+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "410a76c9c225", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9fe68df2e674", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093020", "c": "105", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床生理學與病理學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 72, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-20654', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-093-aca0a627', 'sub-medical-tech-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '人類之基因大約有幾個？ 約1萬個  約3萬個  約5萬個  約7萬個', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:15+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "410a76c9c225", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9fe68df2e674", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093020", "c": "105", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床生理學與病理學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 73, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-20655', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-093-aca0a627', 'sub-medical-tech-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '一個腫瘤裡含有無數個腫瘤細胞，其中很多腫瘤細胞之外形與基因變化都不盡相同，此謂之： 起始作用 (initiation)  混和瘤 (mixed tumor)  多株性 (polyclonality)  異形性 (heterogeneity)', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:15+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "410a76c9c225", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9fe68df2e674", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093020", "c": "105", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床生理學與病理學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 74, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-20656', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-093-aca0a627', 'sub-medical-tech-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '纖維囊泡症 (cystic fibrosis) 是那個管道 (channel) 出問題？ 鈉離子管道 (sodium channel)  鉀離子管道 (potassium channel) 氯離子管道 (chloride channel)  鈣離子管道 (calcium channel)', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:15+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "410a76c9c225", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9fe68df2e674", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093020", "c": "105", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床生理學與病理學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 75, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
